				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><ul><li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Patienter &lt;&nbsp;65 år</li></ul><ul><li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Vid osäkerhet i diagnosen eller i atypiska fall</li></ul><ul><li><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span>Snabbt demensförlopp</li></ul><ul><li><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span>Patienter med uttalade beteendesymtom <br>eller konfusionsattacker</li></ul><ul><li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Misstanke om Lewy body-demens</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>",
